msgstr ""
"Mu ki akoonu ti a tẹjade le jẹ ẹda, ṣiṣatunkọ, fi silẹ fun ijẹrisi ati "
"ṣakoso lori iboju %sAtunṣe Tuntun%s."

#: admin/options.php:1193
msgid "Submit Revision capabilities"
msgstr "Fi Iṣẹ Atunṣe silẹ"

#: admin/options.php:1211
msgid ""
"If the user can't edit the published post, require Submit Revision "
"capabilities (revise_posts, revise_others_pages, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, beere awọn agbara Fi "
